::Kluster::

Kluster swears. "Worse than I thought," he admits. He taps several 
buttons and looks through some reports. "Much worse."

He didn't ask any further questions. The screen in front of him was 
giving him sufficient info.

"Allright, arm the weapons. Shields to full. Let's get ready for an 
attack!"
